---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import Navigation from "@/components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
import MobileMenu from "@/components/MobileMenu.astro"; // Import the new component
import ParallaxTextOverlay from "@/components/ParallaxTextOverlay.astro";
import NavigationPlaceholder from "@/components/NavigationPlaceholder.astro";
import HeroSection from "@/components/HeroSection.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Blog Layout</title>
		<style>
			/* Only keeping CSS that can't be easily converted to Tailwind */
			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				background-color: white;
			}
			.no-scroll {
				overflow: hidden;
			}
			[x-cloak] {
				display: none !important;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body
		x-data="{ scrollPosition: 0, mobileMenuOpen: false }"
		@scroll.window="scrollPosition = window.scrollY"
		class="bg-white"
		:class="{ 'no-scroll': mobileMenuOpen }"
	>
		<Navigation />
		<HeroSection class="bg-black">
			<ParallaxTextOverlay
				text="Some blog entry headline thats quite long"
				slot="background"
			/>
			<NavigationPlaceholder />
			<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-display leading-tight">
				Some blog entry headline that's quite long
			</h1>
			<div class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-300">Published on March 15, 2024</div>
			<div
				class="mt-4 flex flex-nowrap overflow-x-auto sm:flex-wrap sm:justify-center gap-2"
			>
				{
					["Design", "Web Development", "CSS", "JavaScript"].map((tag) => (
						<a
							href={`/tags/${tag.toLowerCase()}`}
							class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white bg-[hsl(0,0%,7%)] hover:text-black tag-pill select-none cursor-pointer flex-shrink-0"
						>
							{tag}
						</a>
					))
				}
			</div>
		</HeroSection>

		<MobileMenu />

		<!-- Content Box with responsive padding -->
		<div
			class="lg:max-w-screen-md mx-auto bg-white text-black -mt-5 sm:-mt-40 relative z-10"
		>
			<div class="max-w-screen-md p-6 sm:p-20 mx-auto">
				<p class="mb-6">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam in dui
					mauris. Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Sed auctor
					neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Ut aliquam sollicitudin iaculis. Praesent ac semper ante. Interdum et
					malesuada fames ac ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Vivamus eget tempor
					dolor.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Donec ut libero pretium, efficitur nisl vel, sagittis elit. Fusce a
					est in odio vehicula fermentum eu vel diam. Etiam non magna id nunc
					tempus scelerisque.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices
					posuere cubilia curae; Donec pharetra, magna vestibulum aliquet
					ultrices, erat tortor sollicitudin mi, sit amet lobortis sapien sapien
					non mi.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Sed turpis tincidunt, lacinia velit tempus, efficitur nisl. Nunc at
					risus sed metus eleifend commodo. Duis vel sem ut eros sodales
					venenatis.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Sed posuere
					consectetur est at lobortis. Aenean eu leo quam. Pellentesque ornare
					sem lacinia quam venenatis vestibulum.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Curabitur blandit tempus porttitor. Nullam quis risus eget urna mollis
					ornare vel eu leo. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id
					elit.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Cras mattis
					consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla
					sed consectetur.
				</p>

				<!-- Extra paragraphs to enable scrolling for parallax effect -->
				<p class="mb-6">
					Morbi leo risus, porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros. Cras
					mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac
					cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa
					justo sit amet risus.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur. Cras justo odio,
					dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta
					gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut
					id elit.
				</p>

				<p class="mb-6">
					Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum. Donec sed odio dui.
					Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla. Nulla vitae elit
					libero, a pharetra augue.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
